<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Verif Store - Digital Marketplace</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{font-family:'Orbitron',sans-serif;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f0f0f,#111827,#0f172a);color:white}
header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:20px 30px}
.logo{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#00ffcc,#6a00ff);-webkit-background-clip:text;color:transparent}
.container{max-width:1100px;margin:auto;padding:40px 20px}
.hero{text-align:center;margin-top:40px;margin-bottom:50px}
.hero h1{font-size:36px;margin-bottom:15px}
.hero p{opacity:0.7}
.games{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:30px}
.card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border-radius:25px;padding:50px 20px;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;transition:0.4s;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);backdrop-filter:blur(10px)}
.card:hover{transform:translateY(-10px);box-shadow:0 0 40px rgba(106,0,255,0.5)}
.icon{font-size:50px;margin-bottom:20px}
.card h2{font-size:28px;margin-bottom:10px}
.card p{opacity:0.7;font-size:14px}
footer{text-align:center;padding:30px;margin-top:80px;opacity:0.5;font-size:12px}
.payment-btn{position:fixed;bottom:20px;right:20px;background:yellow;color:black;padding:15px 20px;border-radius:50px;font-weight:bold;cursor:pointer;box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5)}
.modal{display:none;position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.8);justify-content:center;align-items:center;padding:20px}
.modal-content{background:#111827;padding:30px;border-radius:20px;max-width:500px;width:100%;text-align:center}
.modal-content img{width:100%;border-radius:15px;margin-top:15px}
.close{margin-top:20px;background:red;color:white;padding:10px 15px;border:none;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
<div class="logo">VERIF STORE</div>
</header>

<div class="container">

<div class="hero">
<h1>Digital Currency Marketplace</h1>
<p>Pilih game terlebih dahulu untuk melihat daftar currency yang tersedia.</p>
</div>

<div class="games">

<div class="card" onclick="location.href='growtopia.html'">
<div class="icon">🌱</div>
<h2>Growtopia</h2>
<p>Jual Beli Diamond Lock & Blue Gem Lock dengan proses cepat dan aman.</p>
</div>

<div class="card" onclick="location.href='creativeps.html'">
<div class="icon">💎</div>
<h2>CreativePS</h2>
<p>Topup & Jual Beli Gem Lock, Mray, IGL, Creative Coin dan lainnya.</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="payment-btn" onclick="openPayment()">💳 Metode Pembayaran</div>

<div class="modal" id="paymentModal">
<div class="modal-content">
<h2>Metode Pembayaran</h2>
<p><b>DANA:</b> 0887-4377-04858</p>
<p><b>GoPay:</b> 0813-1549-5903</p>
<p><b>PayPal:</b> farhanfaza02@gmail.com</p>
<p><b>USDT (BEP20):</b><br>0x36DAf416EC3f9dd0B6DE307b7FE807c5940B70eE</p>

<h3 style="margin-top:20px">QRIS</h3>
<p>Scan menggunakan aplikasi e-wallet apapun.</p>
<img src="qris.png" alt="QRIS Verif Store">

<button class="close" onclick="closePayment()">Tutup</button>
</div>
</div>

<footer>
© 2026 Verif Store • Secure • Trusted • Fast Delivery
</footer>

<script>
function openPayment(){
document.getElementById('paymentModal').style.display='flex';
}
function closePayment(){
document.getElementById('paymentModal').style.display='none';
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
